# The github-workflow bundle self-renders a doctor CI workflow here; keep it untracked —
# committing it would add always-failing CI to this repo (the lock is gitignored, so doctor
# would exit 1 on a missing lock) and pushing it needs the `workflow` credential scope.
# CI for this repo itself is a separate, deferred issue.
.github/workflows/wafflestack-doctor.yml
.waffle.lock.json
.waffle.local.yaml

